    "content": "<h1>Mastering React Hooks</h1>\n<p>Hooks revolutionized how we write React components. Let's look at some of the most important ones.</p>\n<h2>useState</h2>\n<p>Manage local state in functional components.</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre style=\"--shiki-light:#24292eff;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#282A36\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"tsx\" data-theme=\"min-light dracula\"><code data-language=\"tsx\" data-theme=\"min-light dracula\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D32F2F;--shiki-dark:#FF79C6\">const</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292EFF;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\"> [</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1976D2;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\">count</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#212121;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1976D2;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\"> setCount</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292EFF;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\">] </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D32F2F;--shiki-dark:#FF79C6\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#50FA7B\"> useState</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292EFF;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1976D2;--shiki-dark:#BD93F9\">0</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292EFF;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\">)</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2>useEffect</h2>\n<p>Handle side effects like data fetching or subscriptions.</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre style=\"--shiki-light:#24292eff;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#282A36\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"tsx\" data-theme=\"min-light dracula\"><code data-language=\"tsx\" data-theme=\"min-light dracula\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#50FA7B\">useEffect</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292EFF;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\">(() </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D32F2F;--shiki-dark:#FF79C6\">=></span><span style