pan><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292EFF;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\"> b)</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#212121;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292EFF;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\"> [a</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#212121;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292EFF;--shiki-dark:#F8F8F2\"> b])</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2>Custom Hooks</h2>\n<p>Build your own hooks to share logic between components.</p>\n<p>Happy coding!</p>",
